## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases present in some sources. The rapidly changing media landscape means that the role of traditional media is continually evolving, and future developments may alter its current standing. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may not fully capture the nuances of traditional media's role in different demographic segments.